# Listerine Card Component
Listerine Card is a group of content which typically features a less than full-size image alongside
supporting content or a call to action (CTA). Cards are commonly used on websites to call out or
offer something to the site visitor.

## Component Variations
The Listerine Card package provides a set of design variants to promote a quicker and easier site build experience:

- Basic Card
- Hero Card
- Horizontal Card
- Vertical Card
- No Title Card
- No Description Card

## Site Builder Details
```jsx
import { as } from '@bodiless/fclasses'
import { CardClean, vitalCard } from '@bodiless/vital-card';
import { listerineCard } from '@kenvue/listerine';

const MyDefaultCard = as(
  listerineCard.Default,
)(CardClean);
```

### Card Variations via Combined Tokens
The Card can be composed of different tokens to create many card variations. These variations include:
- Default
- Hero
- With No Description
- With No Title
- With Horizontal Orientation
- With Vertical Orientation

### 
For example, to create a vertical Card variation you could _extend_ or _override_ `listerineCard.WithVerticalOrientation`:

- The following _extends_ `listerineCard.WithVerticalOrientation`, and adds the provided border and  padding to the wrapper:

  ```jsx
  const WithVerticalCardBorder = asCardToken(listerineCard.WithVerticalOrientation, {
    Theme: {
      Wrapper: 'border border-black',
    },
    Spacing: {
      Wrapper: 'px-4',
    },
  });
  // Then compose the Listerine Default Card with new custom vertical style.
  const VerticalCardWithBorder = as(
    listerineCard.Default,
    WithVerticalCardBorder,
  )(CardClean);
  ```

- The following _overrides_ `listerineCard.WithVerticalOrientation`; it uses all the same domains from
  `WithVerticalOrientation` (except spacing), and these are replaced with larger paddings:

  ```jsx
  const WithVerticalOrientationMoreSpacing = asCardToken({
    ...listerineCard.WithVerticalOrientation,
    Spacing: {
      ContentWrapper: 'p-8',
      ImageWrapper: 'p-8',
    },
  });
  // Then compose the Listerine Default Card with new custom vertical style.
  const VerticalCardWithSpacing = as(
    listerineCard.Default,
    WithVerticalOrientationMoreSpacing,
  )(CardClean);
  ```
